'''Disra's palace''' was an ornate [[palace]] on [[Bastion/Legends|Bastion]] in the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] [[Ravelin]], originally built for the [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] of the [[Braxant sector/Legends|Braxant sector]] during the days of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It was much larger and more luxurious than the typical headquarters of a moff, including [[ivrooy coral]] furniture. By [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], in addition to housing the personal offices and quarters of Moff [[Vilim Disra]], it also housed the [[Moff Assembly Hall|meeting area]] of the [[Council of Moffs/Legends|Council of Moffs]]. Fifty [[Meter/Legends|meters]] below the main building was a [[Torture/Legends|torture]]/dungeon area, as well as a secret escape tunnel to the hills to the north of the complex. Disra had lined the palace with [[Holocamera/Legends|holocams]] accessible from his office.

